LongGammaWrapperStreamia
├── when swaps generate pool fees and the long premium is read
│   ├── it reads longPremium from the accumulated fees getter and never from a per block constant
│   ├── it returns exactly the getter slots from the same call at the same tick proving read fidelity
│   └── it records a non zero streamia for at least one token after swaps cross the chunk
├── when additional swaps generate more fees
│   └── it asserts the recorded streamia is monotonic non decreasing and strictly increases after a material swap
└── when recordStreamia is called outside the Open state
    └── it reverts WrongState both before the position is opened and after it is claimed
